---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Consulting" description="Nathan Bost — AI consulting, speaking, and workshops for individuals, teams, and faith communities.">
  <div class="bg-brand-navy min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">

      <!-- Hero -->
      <header class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-brand-gold text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">AI Consulting</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-cream mb-6 leading-tight">
          Think Clearly About AI.<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Use It Wisely.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/70 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          I help people and organizations understand what AI can actually do — and what it can't.
          The goal isn't to automate everything. It's to build AI into your workflow in a way that
          amplifies what makes you effective without replacing what makes you <em>you</em>.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Services grid -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-gold mb-8">What I Offer</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">⚙</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Workflow Audits</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              A focused look at how you currently work — identifying where AI tools can remove friction,
              save time, and let you focus on higher-value decisions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">🧭</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Tool Selection & Implementation</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Cut through the noise. I help you choose the right tools for your context and get them
              working in a way that actually sticks.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">✍</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Prompt Engineering & Automation</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Practical consulting on getting more out of AI models — writing better prompts,
              building automations, and designing systems that work reliably.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">🎤</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Speaking & Workshops</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Engaging talks and hands-on workshops for businesses, faith communities, and nonprofits —
              covering AI literacy, practical tools, and the ethical questions worth asking.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Speaking callout -->
      <section class="bg-brand-slate/30 border border-brand-gold/20 rounded-xl p-8 mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-gold mb-3">Speaking & Workshops</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I speak on AI adoption, practical automation, and the ethical dimensions of building AI
          into personal and organizational life. I've led workshops for faith communities, small
          businesses, and professional groups — tailored to audiences ranging from skeptics to
          early adopters.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/50 text-sm">
          Available for conferences, church events, leadership retreats, and team training sessions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- TCCC Resources callout -->
      <section class="bg-brand-slate/20 border border-brand-gold/30 rounded-xl p-8 mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-brand-gold text-3xl flex-shrink-0">🏛️</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-gold mb-2">Triangle Christian Chamber — AI Resources</h2>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Attending the Chamber talk on AI? I've put together a curated resource page with
              practical tools, references, and frameworks from the session — organized for easy follow-up.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/ai-tccc"
              class="inline-block bg-brand-gold text-brand-navy font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-gold-light transition-colors text-sm"
            >
              View Chamber AI Resources →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-cream/60 mb-6 text-lg">Ready to start a conversation?</p>
        <a
          href="mailto:nbost130@gmail.com"
          class="inline-block bg-brand-gold text-brand-navy font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-gold-light transition-colors text-lg"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
